      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POLYVANOVA (1) led them up and put them to the sword here last time out, winning comfortably by 1.3L. She only rises 1.5kg for the victory and this looks to shape favourably once again. Can bring up back-to-back victories. SKY RIVER (7) has been super in recent events, finishing behind POLYVANOVA last time out. Cheung remains on board and she meets POLYVANOVA better at the weights this time around. Can feature in the finish once again. SNIP OF GOSSIP (2) missed narrowly two back at Bunbury before a 3.2L defeat at this track most recently. Right back in trip here shouldn't be an issue and Dhurun replaces the apprentice. Won't be far away. RIVERCREST MAGIC (5) finished off strongly first-up over 1300m at this track. She's a track and trip winner in the past and she can go one better today. ROMMEL'S JEUNEY (9) is better than he's shown recently and can feature in the finish.",
